-- Metro Internet Sales to Top 100 Million Euros in 2012, FAZ Says
-- B y   A l e x   W e b b
-- 2012-05-15T07:31:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-15/metro-internet-sales-to-top-100-million-euros-in-2012-faz-says.html
Metro AG (MEO)  expects online sales will
contribute a “significant three-digit-million” figure to
revenue this year and account for 5 percent to 10 percent of all
sales in the medium term,  Frankfurter Allgemeine Zeitung 
reported, citing an interview with Chief Executive Officer Olaf Koch.  There was a “clear improvement” at the company’s brands
in the first quarter, which include Cash & Carry, Media-Saturn,
Real and Galeria Kaufhof, Koch told the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alex Webb in Frankfurt at 
